<h3 style="text-align: center;">Safe hands with Inghams</h3>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13095389/inghams-in-safe-hands-charcoal.png?width=500&amp;height=126.45687645687646" alt="in safe hands" data-udi="umb://media/afba17a916e84fcc848acce5dda4f9c4" /></p>
<p><strong>Extra peace of mind for your next holiday</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>We've been helping you explore your passions for over 90 years.</li>
<li>You're in <a data-udi="umb://document/fa72be9e45bc442089252c6a18a0d2ae" href="/{localLink:umb://document/fa72be9e45bc442089252c6a18a0d2ae}" title="In Safe Hands">safe hands</a> when you book with us and to give you extra peace of mind we've put extra measures in place to help keep you and your money safe.</li>
</ul>
